gantt
    title MVP Feature Build Plan (dependency-driven)
    dateFormat  YYYY-MM-DD
    axisFormat  %d %b
    excludes    weekends

    section Foundations
    PBI-003 Permissioned membership and role management :crit, pbi003, 2026-03-16, 5d
    PBI-020 Shariah governance workflow for PLS approvals :pbi020, 2026-03-16, 5d
    PBI-022 Access logging and cryptographic non-repudiation :crit, pbi022, after pbi003, 5d

    section Core compliance and platform controls
    PBI-002 KYC and AML onboarding workflow :crit, pbi002, after pbi022, 8d
    PBI-005 Immutable audit trail for procure-to-pay events :crit, pbi005, after pbi022, 8d
    PBI-017 Role-based UI and operational dashboards :pbi017, after pbi022, 5d
    PBI-015 Regulator audit reporting and signed export bundle :pbi015, after pbi005, 5d

    section Transaction and PLS workflows
    PBI-006 Order acceptance and escrow contract workflow :crit, pbi006, after pbi005, 8d
    PBI-007 PLS contract model and distribution workflow :crit, pbi007, after pbi006, 8d
    MVP core ready :milestone, mvpready, after pbi007, 0d

    section Deferred MVP scope
    PBI-008 Tokenized receivables issuance and redemption :pbi008, after pbi007, 8d